title: r/Choosingbeggars Need A Babysitter! Paying $0.25/hour 🙏
description:
r/Choosingbeggars Would you take a job that pays $15/hour? What about $10/hour? What about $5/hour? What about... 25 CENTS PER HOUR! That's what a lady is offering babysitters to watch her kids for 12 hours shifts. Lady, if you find somebody willing to watch your kids for 25 cents per hour, then they're definitely not the type of person you want to leave alone with your kids!
